    "benefits_zh": "蜜蜂产生的天然蜡。提供润肤和封闭特性。非常适合唇膏、面霜和固体产品。在皮肤上形成保护屏障。",
    "concerns_en": "Generally very safe. Allergen potential for bee-sensitive individuals. May clog pores in concentrated formulations.",
